{"tid":1532350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[譏諷代替指罵］跟我一齊講： 你地只係讀唔成書既打手 中共既棄卒 人民既公敵","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:54:44.000Z","uid":123713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82c97cc7868b0e338495642b95ad92d07c0daa19","tid":1532350,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"係敵人面前憤怒<br />\n只會令對方覺得得戚<br />\n<br />\n有時候譏諷比憤怒更有效<br />\n用一個<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>&rdquo;我地香港人而家係擺明睇唔起你地&rdquo;</strong></span>既姿態笑尻呢班<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n收納稅人錢 再打納稅人<br />\n讀唔成書走去做打手<br />\n未出學堂就比人洗撚左腦仲自命正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻人工8萬蚊個月 <br />\n遲早比老解2000蚊人工取代既中共棄卒<br />\n冇錯 係$2000啊柒頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到邊都噓聲不斷 <br />\n得班收$300既大媽專程係支那落黎支持你地<br />\n係香港就斷六親<br />\n個仔返學都要保鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地究竟羞唔羞家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩事共產黨只會搵人斬9死你地吸引眼球咋，寫咗遺書準備好瞓浩園未啊condom仔？<br />\n<br />\n唉對唔住 好似深左少少<br />\n你只係一隻連醜字都唔撚識寫既毅進狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"56764d91915c4105cedf5a848353cfe62f969e6f","tid":1532350,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:36:40.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫行動！！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5cBad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5cBad.jpg&h=53535c10&s={SIZE}\" /><i